---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---
<MainLayout title="Instant Day">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <h1 class="text-6xl font-display mb-4">Winners & Nominees</h1>
  <p class="mb-6 text-xl">
    Instant Day was quite a success with more than 500 contributions. So it was difficult to find a winner. After a couple of long but exciting days, the judges agreed on the winner and the 6 nominees.
  </p>
  <section class="mt-20 flex items-start gap-10 border-t border-b p-10">
    <div class="flex-1">

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display mb-2">The winner</h2>
      <p class="font-bold mb-1">Toke and the Goat</p>
      <p class="font-bold mb-1">Submitter: Julie</p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Description/Story: In the vibrant heart of Nørrebro, Toke finds an unexpected companion—a goat with an attitude as bold as the neighborhood itself. Tokes calm curiosity meets the goat's playful stare. (Taken with an Instax Mini)
      </p>
    </div>
    <img src="/winner.webp" alt="winner billede" class="w-40 border rounded shadow" />
  </section>
</div>

     
